ProcessingModuleParamDefinition.Name: Query
ProcessingModuleParamDefinition.Value: SELECT CS.UNID FROM IDS_CASE CS, IDS_PARTICIPANT PP, IDS_PARTY P WHERE PP.CASE_ID=CS.UNID AND PP.PARTY_ID=P.UNID AND CS.STATUS IN (0,1,2,7,8) AND P.MODIFICATION_DATE > CS.MODIFICATION_DATE

ProcessingModuleParamDefinition.Value: Question.INVESTIGATION_STATUS= N; Case.Status=4;

ProcessingModuleParamDefinition.Name: Query
ProcessingModuleParamDefinition.Value: SELECT c.[UNID] FROM [IDS_CASE] c LEFT JOIN [IDS_PRODUCT] p ON c.[PRODUCT_ID] = p.[UNID] LEFT JOIN [IDS_PARTICIPANT] parp ON c.[UNID] = parp.[CASE_ID] LEFT JOIN [IDS_INVESTIGATION] inv ON parp.[UNID] = inv.PARTICIPANT_ID LEFT JOIN [IDS_INVESTIGATION_RESULT] ir ON inv.[UNID] = ir.INVESTIGATION_ID LEFT JOIN [IDS_INVESTIGATION_RESULT_ATTR] ira ON ir.[UNID] = ira.INVESTIGATION_RESULT_ID WHERE 1=1 AND c.[TYPE] = 1 AND c.[STATUS] = 0 AND p.[CODE] = 'RAB' GROUP BY c.[UNID] having MAX(case WHEN ira.[NAME] = 'Result' then ira.[VALUE] End) in ('260385009', '255370002')

ProcessingModuleParamDefinition.Name: Query
ProcessingModuleParamDefinition.Value: SELECT c.[UNID] FROM [IDS_CASE] c JOIN [IDS_PRODUCT] p on c.[PRODUCT_ID] = p.[UNID] JOIN [IDS_EXECUTION_OUTPUT] eo on c.[UNID] = eo.CASE_ID JOIN [IDS_PARTICIPANT] parp ON c.[UNID] = parp.[CASE_ID] JOIN [IDS_PARTY] pty ON parp.[PARTY_ID] = pty.[UNID] JOIN [IDS_CONTACTPOINT] ctp ON pty.[UNID] = ctp.PARTY_ID WHERE 1=1 AND p.CODE = 'WUHAN_NCOV' AND OFFICIAL_PLACE IS NOT NULL group by c.[UNID], c.STATUS, OFFICIAL_PLACE ,c.EXTERNAL_ID HAVING 1=1 AND max(case when eo.VARIABLE = 'COVID_19_PyGeocoder_Jur' then eo.[VALUE] end) IS NULL AND max(case when eo.VARIABLE = 'COVID_19_LabResult' then eo.[VALUE] end) = 'POSITIVE' order by c.EXTERNAL_ID DESC

ProcessingModuleParamDefinition.Name: Query
ProcessingModuleParamDefinition.Value:
select c.UNID
from IDS_CASE c join IDS_PRODUCT pd (nolock) on c.PRODUCT_ID = pd.UNID left join IDS_PARTICIPANT ptp (nolock) on c.UNID = ptp.CASE_ID left join IDS_EXECUTION_OUTPUT eo (nolock) on c.UNID = eo.CASE_ID left join IDS_CONTACTPOINT ctp (nolock) on ptp.PARTY_ID = ctp.PARTY_ID left join IDS_INVESTIGATION inv (nolock) on ptp.UNID = inv.PARTICIPANT_ID where 1=1 and cast(INV.MODIFICATION_DATE as date) between dateadd(day,-2, cast(getdate() AS date)) and cast(getdate() AS date) and ctp.TYPE = 1 group by c.UNID, ctp.OFFICIAL_PLACE having 1=1 and case when (case when max(case when eo.VARIABLE = 'COVID_19_PyGeocoder_Jur' then eo.VALUE end) is null then '' else max(case when eo.VARIABLE = 'COVID_19_PyGeocoder_Jur' then eo.VALUE end) end) <> (case when OFFICIAL_PLACE is null then '' else OFFICIAL_PLACE end ) then 1 else 0 end = 1
